---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
import Container from "@/components/container.astro";
import Sectionhead from "@/components/sectionhead.astro";
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
---

<Layout title="Websites & Apps" description="Websites, booking systems, internal tools, WhatsApp automation, and custom apps for businesses that need things done properly. GDPR-compliant and built for the workflows your team actually runs.">
  <Container>
    <Sectionhead>
      <Fragment slot="title">Websites & Apps</Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="desc">Websites, booking systems, internal tools, and apps for businesses that need things done properly.</Fragment>
    </Sectionhead>

    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl mt-16">
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-lg">
        Web and mobile platforms often look fine on the surface but break
        down the moment they touch sensitive data, regulated workflows, or
        operations that need to be defensible. The pattern is the same
        whether the system handles patient records, client documents, or
        internal financial data: generic builds do not survive contact
        with serious requirements.
      </p>
      <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-lg mt-4">
        AnichLabs OÜ builds web and mobile platforms for businesses that
        need things done properly. From websites with self-hosted booking
        and WhatsApp automation, to internal data platforms and
        customer-facing tools. Every project is built with GDPR-compliant data handling and real
        workflow fit from day one.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl mt-12">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6">What we deliver</h2>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-100">
          <Icon name="uil:browser" class="w-7 h-7 mb-3" style="color: #003399" />
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Websites and Web Platforms</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">Modern, fast, self-hosted websites and web platforms. Booking, dashboards, member areas, e-commerce, internal tools - whatever the project needs, built into the site, no third-party subscriptions.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-100">
          <Icon name="uil:whatsapp" class="w-7 h-7 mb-3" style="color: #003399" />
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">WhatsApp Automation</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">AI-powered conversational agents integrated with your booking system, with frequently-asked-question handling and clean handoff to humans.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-100">
          <Icon name="uil:mobile-android" class="w-7 h-7 mb-3" style="color: #003399" />
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Custom Apps and Internal Tools</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">Customer portals, internal data platforms, and operational apps built for the workflows your team actually runs.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-100">
          <Icon name="uil:lock" class="w-7 h-7 mb-3" style="color: #003399" />
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Sovereign Infrastructure</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">EU hosting, on-premise, or edge - with data residency, role-based access, audit logging, and consent management designed in from the start.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl mt-16">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6">Common questions</h2>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
        <details class="bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 rounded-xl p-5 group">
          <summary class="font-semibold text-gray-800 cursor-pointer list-none flex justify-between items-center text-sm">
            We are a small business. Do you work at our scale?
            <Icon name="uil:angle-down" class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" />
          </summary>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mt-3">Yes. A significant part of our work is with single-location operators and small businesses who need a serious online presence without enterprise overhead. We scope to your size and budget.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 rounded-xl p-5 group">
          <summary class="font-semibold text-gray-800 cursor-pointer list-none flex justify-between items-center text-sm">
            Why not just use WordPress or Wix?
            <Icon name="uil:angle-down" class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" />
          </summary>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mt-3">For a basic brochure site, those tools are fine. For booking, WhatsApp automation, GDPR for sensitive data, or any custom workflow, off-the-shelf platforms become expensive, slow, and hard to maintain. We build modern static and headless architectures that are faster, more secure, and cost less to run.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 rounded-xl p-5 group">
          <summary class="font-semibold text-gray-800 cursor-pointer list-none flex justify-between items-center text-sm">
            Do you offer ongoing maintenance?
            <Icon name="uil:angle-down" class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" />
          </summary>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mt-3">Yes. Every project includes a 12-month warranty for functional issues. Ongoing maintenance, new features, and evolutionary updates are available on retainer or per-engagement.</p>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl mt-16 mb-10 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800">Need a serious platform built right?</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-500 mt-3">Book a free 30-minute call to discuss your project and what a proper build looks like for your situation.</p>
      <a href="https://calendly.com/chris-anichlabs/30min" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
        class="mt-6 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-white font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-lg transition-colors"
        style="background-color: #003399">
        <Icon name="uil:calendar-alt" class="w-5 h-5" />
        Book a Free Call
      </a>
    </div>

  </Container>
</Layout>
